adams.flow.control.Flow
	-annotation
	The SwitchedSource can be used to generate data from different sources, \nwhich get chosen based on the defined boolean conditions.
	-actor
		adams.flow.source.ForLoop
	-actor
		adams.flow.transformer.SetVariable
			-var-name
			var
	-actor
		adams.flow.control.Trigger
			-name
			generate output based on variable
			-tee
				adams.flow.source.SwitchedSource
					-condition
						adams.flow.condition.bool.Expression
							-expression
							(@{var} % 3) = 1
					-case
						adams.flow.source.MathExpression
							-expression
							@{var} * 2
					-case
						adams.flow.source.MathExpression
							-name
							MathExpression-1
							-expression
							@{var} * 100
			-tee
				adams.flow.sink.Display
					-writer
						adams.data.io.output.NullWriter
	-flow-execution-listener
		adams.flow.execution.NullListener

